# Fluff Date: 2026-03-18 15:07:44
<overview>
<p>Conventional infantry within the FWLM serve as the backbone of provincial defense across a patchwork of semi-autonomous states, each maintaining its own military traditions and equipment preferences. Towing crew-served LB 10-X autocannon, these platoons deploy one of the most tactically flexible field guns available, switching between armor-piercing slugs and cluster munitions depending on the target.</p>
</overview>

